cs.LG, cs.SY, cs.IT, cs.DS, cs.AI

The paper deals with online prediction in a linear dynamical system, which involves machine learning and control theory. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also deals with stability and perturbations in the system, which falls under the category of cs.SY (Systems and Control). The paper uses least-squares algorithm and Kalman filter, which are related to information theory and signal processing, respectively, and hence, the paper could also belong to cs.IT (Information Theory) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). Finally, the paper deals with online prediction, which is a subfield of reinforcement learning, and hence, the paper could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
